  "operation_name": "aclnnAdaptiveMaxPool2dBackward",
  "description": "算子功能：正向自适应最大池化的反向传播，将梯度回填到每个自适应窗口最大值的坐标处，相同坐标处累加。\n正向计算公式：对于输入self维度$[N,C,H,W]$，N（Batch）表示批量大小、C（Channels）表示特征图通道、H（Height）表示特征图高度、W（Width）表示特征图宽度，outputSize值为$[H_o,W_o]$的场景，其输出output维度为$[N,C,H_o,W_o]$，索引indices维度为$[N,C,H_o,W_o]$，相应tensor中每个元素的计算公式如下：\n$$\nH_{left}^m = \\lfloor(m*H)/H_o\\rfloor \\\\\nH_{right}^m = \\lceil(m*H)/H_o\\rceil  \\\\\nW_{left}^n = \\lfloor(n*W)/W_o\\rfloor \\\\\nW_{right}^n = \\lceil(n*W)/W_o\\rceil  \\\\\noutput(N,C,l,m,n) = \\mathop{\\max}\\limits_{i \\in ,j\\in[H_{left}^m,H_{right}^m],k\\in[W_{left}^n,W_{right}^n]} input(N,C,i,j,k) \\\\\nindices(N,C,l,m,n) = \\mathop{\\arg\\max}\\limits_{i \\in ,j\\in[H_{left}^m,H_{right}^m],k\\in[W_{left}^n,W_{right}^n]} input(N,C,i,j,k)\n$$",
  "api_flow": "two-step",
  "inter_parameter_constraints": [
    {
      "type": "shape_equality",
      "params": [
        "gradOutput",
        "indices"
      ],
      "expr": "gradOutput.shape == indices.shape",
      "description": "gradOutput 与 indices 的 shape 必须一致。",
      "source": "gradOutput",
      "target": [
        "indices"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_equality",
      "params": [
        "self",
        "gradInput"
      ],
      "expr": "self.shape == gradInput.shape",
      "description": "self 与 gradInput 的 shape 必须一致。",
      "source": "self",
      "target": [
        "gradInput"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_dependency",
      "params": [
        "self",
        "gradOutput"
      ],
      "expr": "self.shape[:-2] == gradOutput.shape[:-2]",
      "description": "self 与 gradOutput 除后两个维度外的前置维度必须一致，对应相同的 batch 和 channel 维。",
      "source": "self",
      "target": [
        "gradOutput"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "format_equality",
      "params": [
        "gradOutput",
        "indices"
      ],
      "expr": "gradOutput.format == indices.format",
      "description": "indices 的数据格式必须与 gradOutput 保持一致。",
      "source": "gradOutput",
      "target": [
        "indices"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "format_equality",
      "params": [
        "self",
        "gradInput"
      ],
      "expr": "self.format == gradInput.format",
      "description": "gradInput 的数据格式必须与 self 保持一致。",
      "source": "self",
      "target": [
        "gradInput"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_value_dependency",
      "params": [
        "self",
        "gradOutput"
      ],
      "expr": "((self.shape[-2] % gradOutput.shape[-2] == 0) and (self.shape[-1] % gradOutput.shape[-1] == 0)) or (self.shape[-2] <= 2**24 and self.shape[-1] <= 2**24 and gradOutput.shape[-2] <= 2**24 and gradOutput.shape[-1] <= 2**24)",
      "description": "当 self 后两个维度分别能被 gradOutput 后两个维度整除时没有额外限制；非整除场景下，self 和 gradOutput 后两个维度的维度值都不能超过 2^24。",
      "source": "self",
      "target": [
        "gradOutput"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_value_dependency",
      "params": [
        "self",
        "indices"
      ],
      "expr": "self.shape[-2] * self.shape[-1] <= 2**31 - 1",
      "description": "self 的 height 与 width 的乘积不能超过 max int32，否则会超出 indices 的表示范围。",
      "source": "self",
      "target": [
        "indices"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "platform_specifics": [
    {
      "platform": "Atlas A3 训练系列产品/Atlas A3 推理系列产品",
      "description": "是否支持：√",
      "constraint_detail": "supported == True"
    },
    {
      "platform": "Atlas A2 训练系列产品/Atlas A2 推理系列产品",
